    "en": "So Allah, Mighty and Majestic, revealed to him: 'This is your son David; his age is forty years, and I have indeed written the lifespans, distributed the provisions, and I obliterate what I will and affirm (what I will), and with Me is the Mother of the Book. So if you make something of your lifespan for him, I shall attach it to him.' He (Adam) said: 'O Lord! I have made sixty years from my lifespan for him, to complete one hundred.'",
